---
// Componente CTA para la página de sponsors
---

<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900 to-blue-800 py-16 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Patrón decorativo -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <defs>
        <pattern id="dot-pattern" x="0" y="0" width="10" height="10" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <circle cx="5" cy="5" r="1" fill="currentColor"/>
        </pattern>
      </defs>
      <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#dot-pattern)"/>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 border border-white/20 shadow-lg">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">¿Interesado en ser sponsor?</h2>
        <p class="text-blue-100 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Únete a InnovaTech Ica 2025 como patrocinador y posiciona tu marca en el centro de la innovación tecnológica de la región.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-5 text-center border border-white/20">
          <div class="text-blue-100 text-4xl mb-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-lg mb-2">Networking Premium</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm">Conecta con profesionales, líderes y potenciales clientes del sector tecnológico</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-5 text-center border border-white/20">
          <div class="text-blue-100 text-4xl mb-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8.688c0-.864.933-1.405 1.683-.977l7.108 4.062a1.125 1.125 0 010 1.953l-7.108 4.062A1.125 1.125 0 013 16.81V8.688zM12.75 8.688c0-.864.933-1.405 1.683-.977l7.108 4.062a1.125 1.125 0 010 1.953l-7.108 4.062a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.683-.977V8.688z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-lg mb-2">Visibilidad de Marca</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm">Exposición de tu marca ante una audiencia cualificada e interesada en tecnología</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-5 text-center border border-white/20">
          <div class="text-blue-100 text-4xl mb-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 18.75h-9m9 0a3 3 0 013 3h-15a3 3 0 013-3m9 0v-3.375c0-.621-.503-1.125-1.125-1.125h-.871M7.5 18.75v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h.872m5.007 0H9.497m5.007 0a7.454 7.454 0 01-.982-3.172M9.497 14.25a7.454 7.454 0 00.981-3.172M5.25 4.236c-.982.143-1.954.317-2.916.52A6.003 6.003 0 007.73 9.728M5.25 4.236V4.5c0 2.108.966 3.99 2.48 5.228M5.25 4.236V2.721C7.456 2.41 9.71 2.25 12 2.25c2.291 0 4.545.16 6.75.47v1.516M7.73 9.728a6.726 6.726 0 002.748 1.35m8.272-6.842V4.5c0 2.108-.966 3.99-2.48 5.228m2.48-5.492a46.32 46.32 0 012.916.52 6.003 6.003 0 01-5.395 4.972m0 0a6.726 6.726 0 01-2.749 1.35m0 0a6.772 6.772 0 01-3.044 0" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-lg mb-2">Posicionamiento</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-100 text-sm">Posiciona tu organización como líder e innovadora en el sector tecnológico</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/contacto" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-blue-700 bg-white hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1 duration-200">
          Contáctanos para ser sponsor
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>